      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh really? i thought it was a myth. i read somewhere that as long as u dont drink like, a whole liter of it at once, it's okay. like, if i just have a small amount, it shouldn't really change my blood levels that much right? it seems a bit extreme to avoid it completely if i'm just having a normal serving.",
