      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get the enzyme thing but i've been feeling a bit tired lately and i really need the vitamin c from the juice to help with my energy. if i just take my pill in the morning and wait like 4 or 5 hours before i drink the juice, does that solve the problem? it seems like if they aren't in my stomach at the exact same time, there shouldn't be an issue.",
